	<li class="comment odd alt depth-2" id="li-comment-681883">
		<div class="commentBackgroundizer">
			<div class="commentLiner" id="comment-681883">
				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/a9191a33863d37c3ece70c0ea6da6dce?s=50&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.marksdailyapple.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2FmarksDailyApple%2Fimages%2FgrokGravatar.png%3Fs%3D50&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-50 photo' height='50' width='50' />				<div class="commentContent">
										<p>Cholesterol absorption is non-linear at as dietary cholesterol increases.  The absorption pathway becomes saturated and a lower relative amount actually gets absorbed as the amount eaten increases.  What&#8217;s not absorbed passes through in the end (pun intended).</p>
				</div>
				<div class="clearMe"></div>
