<p>Often cited, but no real evidence of a correlation or a danger of eating sat fats<br />
This is one of my favorite quotes:<br />
&#8220;For example, in Framingham, Mass, the more saturated fat one ate, the more cholesterol one ate, the more calories one ate, the lower the persons serum cholesterol.&#8221;<br />
This is from the then Director of the study!</p>
